Haigh diagrams depict fatigue failure curves in <math> \sigma_a, \sigma_m </math> -space.  The failure curves correspond to specific life lengths, <math>n</math>. <br><br>

[[File:Haigh.JPG|thumb|center|600px|A simple Haigh diagram]]












