==Configuration== [[Image:Transistor_amplifier_blocked_emitor.svg|300px|thumb|left|Circuit without resistors R<sub>1</sub>, R<sub>2</sub>]] {{clear}} ==Analysis== :<math>V_B = V_i </math> :<math>V_E = V_B - 0.7 = V_B</math> :<math>I_E = \frac {V_E} {R_4} = \frac {V_B} {R_4}</math> :<math>I_C = I_E</math> :<math>V_C = V_C - I_C R_3</math>
